snippet.title: Honey, I Joined A Cult Partnership Trailer
snippet.description:
We’re thrilled to announce that we’ve partnered with Soul Survivor Games to bring Honey, I Joined a Cult to PC! (Please note art shown in video is not final)

Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/841190/Honey_I_Joined_a_Cult/
Learn More: https://bit.ly/HIJACPartnership

Honey, I Joined a Cult puts players in charge of creating, operating, and growing a cult in the funky 1970s! Your duties range from choosing the organisation’s symbols, relics, and merchandise, to recruiting new acolytes and deciding where the toilets should be at the compound.

Sole Survivor Games website: https://www.solesurvivorgames.com/
Follow Sole Survivor Games on Twitter: https://twitter.com/solesurvivorgms
Follow Sole Survivor Games on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/solesurvivorgames/ 
Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/

#HoneyIJoinedACult  #Team17 #IndieGame #HIJAC

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Aven Colony, The Escapists, Genesis Alpha One, Overcooked, Sword Legacy: Omen, Yoku’s Island Express, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. Visit www.team17.com for more info.
